# FILE: HomePage.desc
# ROLE: Master Layout & Logic for HalabUnver Hub (Unified Ecosystem)

## 1. VISUAL IDENTITY & SCIENTIFIC THEME
- BRANDING: HalabUnver (Aleppo University Ecosystem).
- THEME: Seamless Light/Dark toggle (Tailwind v4 `dark:` prefix).
- DESIGN: Rigid 90-degree grid, white-outline boxes, high-contrast.
- VIBE: "Scientific/Academic Dashboard" (Technical chips, Monospace data).
- TYPOGRAPHY: Modern Arabic (RTL) + Professional Sans-Serif English.

## 2. NAVIGATION & HEADER (The Hub)
- STICKY NAV: Constant visibility.
- HEADER_ACTION: High-contrast **[ 📢 الأخبار ]** (News) button.
  - **DYNAMICS:** Admin-controlled state. If `isExamSeason === true` -> Color: **RED** (Pulse), Action: Redirect to `/exam-hub`.
  - **DEFAULT:** Color: Brand Accent, Action: Open News/Scroll to News Section.
- UNIVERSAL SEARCH (HUD INTERFACE):
  - TRIGGER: Clicking search input expands a "Floating HUD Overlay."
  - BEHAVIOR: Dims/blurs the background Home Page content.
  - UI: Floating results dropdown with "Category Icons" (Book, Gear, Job).
  - SCOPE: Queries /api/v1/search/* (Aggregates Store, Library, Talent).
  - OVERFLOW: A "See All Results" button links to the [Search Archive] sub-page.
- ATTRACTION LINKS: Academy, Library, Store, Talent, GPA Tracker.

## 3. DYNAMIC CONTENT SECTIONS (Admin Controlled)
- SECTION [HERO]: Brand Identity ("Challenge Every Day").
- SECTION [ECOSYSTEM_ANALYTICS]: High-tech "Status Board" with real-time counters.
- SECTION [OFFERS]: Universal space for Courses, Certs, or Physical Gear.
  - STYLE: Multi-style sections (Banners, Cards, Highlights).
  - MEDIA: **STRICTLY URL-BASED IMAGES.**
- SECTION [NEWS]: Journalistic/Academic feed with Monospace ISO Dates.
- SECTION [PILLARS]: 4 high-impact cards with "Live Stats."

## 4. FOOTER & UI UTILITIES
- SOCIAL & CONTACT: Full icon set + Support Email + Academic links.
- DEVELOPER SIGNATURE: [ Ahmed Al-Jassem ] (AMJ) High-contrast Button.
- UTILITY: "Back to Top" 90-degree square button (Binary/Coordinate icon).
- SYSTEM BAR: Micro-footer with `[ SYSTEM: STABLE ]` and `[ VERSION: 2026.1 ]`.

## 5. ARCHITECTURE NOTE (ATOMIC COMPONENTS)
- **MODULARITY: Every repeatable UI element (OfferCard, NewsCard, PillarCard, SearchDropdown, AMJButton) must be a standalone component in `/src/components/`.**
- **SECTIONS: The major layout blocks (Hero, Analytics, OffersSection) will also be components that "map" to the Home Page layout.**
- ASSETS: SVGs for icons; optimized RTL font loading.